def_cn: 无人地带;无人管辖地区
def_en: No-man's land is an area of land that is not owned or controlled by anyone, for example the area of land between two opposing armies.

def_cn: 尚未确定的情况;中间状态
def_en: If you refer to a situation as a no-man's land between different things, you mean that it seems unclear because it does not fit into any of the categories.
